{"tid":438282,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"教你點對付地鐵仆街仔","createTime":"2017-10-16T18:42:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T11:29:24.000Z","uid":78569,"like":173,"dislike":554,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"a692aac1e0dac42204bd05b94a74e9fc09cd8638","tid":438282,"uid":78569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T18:42:32.000Z","msg":"地鐵有好多仆街仔好無教養好無禮貌，呢篇文教你點對付佢！<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/8gdt2rhc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F8gdt2rhc&h=852684b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n古語有云：要對付奸人，就要比他更奸。<br />\n所以依家教你點樣比班仆街仔更仆街、更無教養、更無禮貌！<br />\n<br />\n（仆街仔1&mdash;欖球員）<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/areuq80i\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fareuq80i&h=207d1be4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喺繁忙時間，車箱入面人山人海，呢啲人為求出站，會無視周圍嘅障礙，突破重圍！就好似一個欖球員一樣，眼中只有得分線，無論乜嘢人都要將佢哋撞開！為求達陣！<br />\n<br />\n對付方法：唔好同佢硬碰，都唔好入佢中路，通常呢啲人都有番咁上下身型。我建議以退為進，退後至車門，車門位置空間較多，首先睇凖時機避開、再伸出右腳、腳踝貼地、腳尖抬起！順利的話就可以將佢於車門外絆倒！當佢想起身屌你老母既時候，車門就會剛剛好關上，你可以安全喺車入面報以一絲微笑高舉中指。<br />\n<br />\n（仆街仔2&mdash;處男）<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/orlem6nj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Forlem6nj&h=adf1fe1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n顧名思義就係&rdquo;埃&rdquo;住條柱嘅仆街仔，一個人霸哂條柱令你無法入手。<br />\n<br />\n對付方法：首先你要拎起電話扮聽電話，好似完全留意唔到佢咁。然後你再扯緊你的手指，好似龍抓手咁對住佢埃住條柱嘅&rdquo;尾龍骨&rdquo;一野抓落去！！佢就會痛到「啊」一聲。呢個時候你要扮傾住電話同佢講：OH～I am sorry~<br />\n如果佢係背囊埃住，就扮捉錯咗佢背囊，然後全力向下一拉！因為佢原本重心喺哂條柱度，所以你一拉佢就會失重心，成個人仆左喺度。當然呢個時候你要扮傾住電話同佢講：OH～I am sorry~<br />\n<br />\n（仆街仔3&mdash;死人霸生地）<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/8y1bvim4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F8y1bvim4&h=793f1223&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢D人會將佢的死物（例如：背囊、貨物、手袋）霸住個位，即使你行到佢隔離，佢都係完全無反應唔會拎開佢的死物，正一死人霸生地。<br />\n<br />\n對付方法：首先你又係要拎起電話扮聽電話，好似完全留意唔到咁，最好加多句對白：「唉～又OT真係好攰呀～」然後扮哂全身無力咁一野坐落去！（扮全身無力，但其實係用盡全力。注意唔係&quot;坐&quot;落去，係&quot;轟&quot;落去）重點係要將佢放上坐位的所有野壓扁！當然呢個時候你又要扮傾住電話同佢講：OH～I am sorry~<br />\n<br />\n（仆街仔4&mdash;背囊的觸手）<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/fe9y2wju\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ffe9y2wju&h=ec7cdbcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n觸手唔只係AV情節出現，都出現喺地鐵入面。大家用過背囊都知，背囊有好多觸手（背囊的繩）。當然好多人坐底都會好有禮貌咁收埋佢，但有D仆街仔就放任D觸手自由探索，撫摸美女的大腿，鑽入迷人的股間⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n對付方法：嗯⋯⋯我都唔知，但以下係我真人真事。<br />\n<br />\n我首次遇到呢D觸手仆街仔，我用咗對付（仆街仔3&mdash;死人霸生地）的方法，一野轟落去，但事主毫無感覺。我大吃一驚！我唔知道應該點去應對！我好迷惘。<br />\n就在我閉目沉思的時候，個仆街仔用力扯個背囊！背囊的觸手就喺我股間左右穿梭，我誓不投降！我用我的可控制肌肉將觸手夾住！！股間有咩肌肉係可控制？無錯就係我肛門的括約肌！<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/8h2a9fjb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F8h2a9fjb&h=1902f8f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我好似忍屎咁夾實，但我要合起雙眼扮瞓教！<br />\n大家的拉拉扯扯中，地鐵已到達終點站。<br />\n我的括約肌用盡最後一絲力氣，起身！我將佢的背囊連根拔起！佢的背囊跌左喺地下。<br />\n我幫佢拎起地上還有我肛門氣息的背囊講咗句⋯⋯OH～I am sorry~<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/Etx9ry\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FEtx9ry&d=%2BfSyTHw2z6m6eDouurFZdU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=3af4bfb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/Etx9ry</a><br />\n<br />\n新手fb page，文筆好弱。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65736cf87eb5d2e30a96d2eadb390c77bc86cad7","tid":438282,"uid":78569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T18:42:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64e34979c058b915b977e9ac8c1b53717ddbcc2e","tid":438282,"uid":78569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T18:52:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"707219008ba78fed6de0e66775d207b851695525","tid":438282,"uid":140334,"like":3,"dislike":13,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T18:54:26.000Z","msg":"笑左 下次試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a94a2ce579c96cd96d9efabc8a71e799963dff22","tid":438282,"uid":2419,"like":72,"dislike":1,"score":71,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T18:54:58.000Z","msg":"見你打咁多野又推晒圖又冇人理 幫人推下"},{"pid":"425cc36514898fa18d61a6e55f29c259024fe004","tid":438282,"uid":30934,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T18:59:39.000Z","msg":"點對付搭地鐵挨身挨勢個啲？<br />\n即係人貼人時 借你個身黎挨個啲"},{"pid":"53dbf312f565f80b7c3d3a8f83a6e919044c626e","tid":438282,"uid":28862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T19:00:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">AA</span>"},{"pid":"8fa02bb7b8f1b9a6790f61ff4e179b8765a6d7e0","tid":438282,"uid":78569,"like":0,"dislike":39,"score":-39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T19:08:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見你打咁多野又推晒圖又冇人理 幫人推下</blockquote><br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果like一like個page就更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9411ff112c83a505d6b4dfb2c885b64946afc608","tid":438282,"uid":75694,"like":199,"dislike":2,"score":197,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T19:08:23.000Z","msg":"想sell自己個page <br />\n不了 OH~~I am so sorry ~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2e91d3577823a1fda102a2e332913fd3756e7ed","tid":438282,"uid":87511,"like":109,"dislike":3,"score":106,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T19:10:08.000Z","msg":"欖球員有乜問題<br />\n你條撚樣阻鳩住人落車仲好意思講<br />\n<br />\n腐皮"},{"pid":"2b6394356700834fd4c3b463d0ff4731dbc87dc8","tid":438282,"uid":27416,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T19:12:02.000Z","msg":"有無教點對付上連登宣傳fb page 仆街仔"},{"pid":"3d851e2398d3d5d20b8b6ffac4f42ccbfdbea1fe","tid":438282,"uid":78569,"like":1,"dislike":37,"score":-36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T19:12:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想sell自己個page <br />\n不了 OH~~I am so sorry ~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個page我又無錢賺既，只係比個目標自己，想大家支持下，比D動力我姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92bb461a09fa5f638f6a582a92972b13089926d0","tid":438282,"uid":78569,"like":3,"dislike":32,"score":-29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T19:13:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無教點對付上連登宣傳fb page 仆街仔</blockquote><br />\nlike左佢個page再PM條仆街講屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29a19830ee420daffff0f7ea33f7db815742a4fd","tid":438282,"uid":87511,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T19:14:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>欖球員有乜問題<br />\n你條撚樣阻鳩住人落車仲好意思講<br />\n<br />\n腐皮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n繁忙時間喺九龍塘大圍太子呢啲站轉車，永遠畀一堆柒頭廢老廢中大陸閪阻撚住我落車<br />\n好似真係唔會識先落後上<br />\n<br />\n唔撚撞開佢哋點得？"},{"pid":"331feb2b73f77b2b193f54d06cae5aba21877358","tid":438282,"uid":78569,"like":0,"dislike":46,"score":-46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T19:14:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>欖球員有乜問題<br />\n你條撚樣阻鳩住人落車仲好意思講<br />\n<br />\n腐皮</blockquote><br />\n唔該都唔識講，把口生出黎淨係幫人含撚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"689eebf3bb08eb94d8eecc854e7241de4711599c","tid":438282,"uid":78569,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T19:15:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>欖球員有乜問題<br />\n你條撚樣阻鳩住人落車仲好意思講<br />\n<br />\n腐皮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n繁忙時間喺九龍塘大圍太子呢啲站轉車，永遠畀一堆柒頭廢老廢中大陸閪阻撚住我落車<br />\n好似真係唔會識先落後上<br />\n<br />\n唔撚撞開佢哋點得？</blockquote><br />\n咁呢D又撞得啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8be81ececbe80c661632ef7442b08bc56d10e7db","tid":438282,"uid":87511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T19:16:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>欖球員有乜問題<br />\n你條撚樣阻鳩住人落車仲好意思講<br />\n<br />\n腐皮</blockquote><br />\n唔該都唔識講，把口生出黎淨係幫人含撚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔通你就係下下企正車門中間、阻人落車嗰堆？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6141285f3f493158b441baed9d76c6404e139770","tid":438282,"uid":15984,"like":104,"dislike":1,"score":103,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T19:17:44.000Z","msg":"屌你好撚ON9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一啲都唔好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成個白痴仔咁自言自語<br />\n想拎共嗚引正評唔係咁樣<br />\n<br />\n屌真係好ON9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c87bf8a9e42c5ffcdafd0599f507b38247fc97","tid":438282,"uid":131926,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T19:20:39.000Z","msg":"尿道同肛門都未識分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e9bf1a57db504cbd9d392fe206bb82e018e63d0","tid":438282,"uid":87511,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T19:20:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你好撚ON9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一啲都唔好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成個白痴仔咁自言自語<br />\n想拎共嗚引正評唔係咁樣<br />\n<br />\n屌真係好ON9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n欖球員嗰度已經夠戇鳩啦<br />\n又唔諗下點解自己會畀人撞<br />\n企埋一邊等人落哂先、唔好阻人落車是常識吧"},{"pid":"92e8dfb0383bd2cdf1c0b758f985e77828e55ab4","tid":438282,"uid":78569,"like":0,"dislike":22,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T19:22:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>欖球員有乜問題<br />\n你條撚樣阻鳩住人落車仲好意思講<br />\n<br />\n腐皮</blockquote><br />\n唔該都唔識講，把口生出黎淨係幫人含撚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔通你就係下下企正車門中間、阻人落車嗰堆？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係霸住個關愛座做生意果堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實無呀，其實我想講禮貌小小得唔得，已經好迫仲要聲都唔聲就撞咗先，好無禮貌囉。<br />\n仲要撞跌我電話！裂撚左mon啦！"},{"pid":"472ce32cee997ebb901cc2591e0ae959f9f44d0f","tid":438282,"uid":47628,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T19:22:46.000Z","msg":"Sorry樓主你嗰張係膀肛圖好似唔係肛門嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bfa989738d67189bf39abed4868c23c5f0e474a","tid":438282,"uid":78569,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T19:23:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>尿道同肛門都未識分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n盲生。。。你突破了。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffeb185bb33d1be3ff9a8f884c5df8f9c15d7f03","tid":438282,"uid":78569,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T19:24:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Sorry樓主你嗰張係膀肛圖好似唔係肛門嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係wo屌，笑咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> sorry"},{"pid":"12647d742d4119b7c73d16e90703e9d43cf21a1f","tid":438282,"uid":65425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T19:25:02.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"1621aa6aaf06a3733b7db033f22d44f7c407e1e1","tid":438282,"uid":78569,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyT